trans-unit.source: allow_reload Specifies whether the client can force a cache reload by including a Cache-Control "no-cache" directive in the request. Set it to true for compliance with RFC 2616. (default: false)

allow_revalidate Specifies whether the client can force a cache revalidate by including a Cache-Control "max-age=0" directive in the request. Set it to true for compliance with RFC 2616. (default: false)
